Text: My good and holy Kamisama. Even more priceless garbage! You are the Jesus of Junk movies. You are the Badass of BAD! MaiWhang is deeply moved and deeply happy to see all of this great crap! May bad movies live on.
More ungodly garbage. I am in your debt forever...and ever. Keep bring these great movies out. MaiWhang is in a happy place, watching your great vids.
